    "95807316": {
      "title": "Polymer brushes: surface-immobilized macromolecules",
      "abstract": "This article reviews recent literature on polymer brushes with an emphasis on linear polymer brushes attached to solid substrate surfaces. The following topics are included: (i) theoretical and experimental studies of homopolymer brush structure; (ii) theoretical investigations of diblock copolymer brushes; (iii) preparation of homopolymer brushes by physisorption, “grafting to” and “grafting from” methods; (iv) synthesis of diblock copolymer brushes; and (v) fabrication of patterned polymer brushes."
